packageJson.name: @oods/trait-engine
packageJson.description: Object-Oriented Design System Trait Composition Engine

scripts.pretest:coverage: pnpm run build && pnpm run build:packages
scripts.ci:local: npm run lint && npm run test:unit && npm run test:integration && npm run test:validation && npm run validate:pipeline && npm run tokens-validate && npm run test:contrast && npm run test:coverage
scripts.tokens-validate: pnpm run tokens:validate && pnpm run tokens:lint-semantic && pnpm run tokens:guardrails -- --quiet
scripts.pipeline:push: pnpm run build:tokens && pnpm run build-storybook && (pnpm run chromatic || echo chromatic skipped) && pnpm run vrt:hc && pnpm run current-state:sprint08 && pnpm run validate:contexts && pnpm run purity:audit
